{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3@4.pkg/1772602362321/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602363382", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3@4.pkg/1772602362321/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602363382"}, "identifier": "2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】诗中的“明月”作者没有将其看成是友好的使者，而是以青山明月自许，表现了对人生高洁的追求。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】闻王昌龄左迁龙标遥有此寄 李白</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>杨花落尽子规啼，闻道龙标过五溪。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>我寄愁心与明月，随君直到夜郎西。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】龙标野宴 王昌龄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>沅溪夏晚足凉风，春酒相携就竹丛。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>莫道弦歌愁远谪，青山明月不曾空。</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】闻王昌龄左迁龙标遥有此寄 李白杨花落尽子规啼，闻道龙标过五溪。我寄愁心与明月，随君直到夜郎西。【乙】龙标野宴 王昌龄沅溪夏晚足凉风，春酒相携就竹丛。莫道弦歌愁远谪，青山明月不曾空。", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3@4.pkg/item.json?v=1751940015893", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>甲诗中的“杨花”、“子规”两种景物，点明了时令。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>乙诗中的“愁”是远谪之愁，诗人以“愁”衬托出自己不以远谪为念、寄情山水之情。</span></p>\n</div>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>借明月来抒发怀人感情是古诗中常见的手法，两首诗中的&ldquo;明月&rdquo;都是将其人格化，把它看成是友好的使者。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>李诗中的&ldquo;闻道&rdquo;可见诗人得知挚友被贬时的惊愕痛惜之情；王诗中的&ldquo;莫道&rdquo;只是&ldquo;不要说&rdquo;而已，其实心中并没有放下。</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】闻王昌龄左迁龙标遥有此寄 李白</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>杨花落尽子规啼，闻道龙标过五溪。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>我寄愁心与明月，随君直到夜郎西。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】龙标野宴 王昌龄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>沅溪夏晚足凉风，春酒相携就竹丛。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>莫道弦歌愁远谪，青山明月不曾空。</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "6a749654-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "5136342960", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是（　　）【甲】闻王昌龄左迁龙标遥有此寄 李白杨花落尽子规啼，闻道龙标过五溪。我寄愁心与明月，随君直到夜郎西。【乙】龙标野宴 王昌龄沅溪夏晚足凉风，春酒相携就竹丛。莫道弦歌愁远谪，青山明月不曾空。"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列对两首诗的理解和分析不正确的一项是</span><span>（</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">　　</span><span>）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【甲】闻王昌龄左迁龙标遥有此寄 李白</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>杨花落尽子规啼，闻道龙标过五溪。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>我寄愁心与明月，随君直到夜郎西。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>【乙】龙标野宴 王昌龄</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>沅溪夏晚足凉风，春酒相携就竹丛。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>莫道弦歌愁远谪，青山明月不曾空。</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/2e197895-eeeb-4d5c-a436-936fed2573f3@4.pkg/1772602362321/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602363382", "question_small": "https: